<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>[ . .  . ] of Zenon son of Zenon [ . . . of ?The]mison son of Zenon son of Adrastos, in which sarcophagus shall be buried the afore-mentioned Zenon and Aurelia Charition daughter of Kallikrates <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/></p>
</div>
<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p>The text was clearly continued on the sarcophagus. It is probable that the edict of Caracalla occurred within the lifetime of these persons.</p>
</div>
